MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: -- As part of ITPR017177 Rebates Copy/Void Rewrite, re-wrote the entire code to load new and changed claims from EXTN_CLM_STG table and update retained claims and dropped using post sql.
MAPPING.NAME: m_CASH_InsertUpdate_RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM_CopyVoid

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select EXT.RECN_GID AS RECN_GID, EXT.CLM_GID AS CLM_GID, EXT.RPT_ID AS RPT_ID, EXT.ADMN_DISC_APC_AMT AS ADMN_DISC_APC_AMT, EXT.BASE_DISC_APC_AMT AS BASE_DISC_APC_AMT, EXT.CTRC_DISC_APC_AMT AS CTRC_DISC_APC_AMT, EXT.FRMLY_DISC_APC_AMT AS FRMLY_DISC_APC_AMT, EXT.PERF_DISC_APC_AMT AS PERF_DISC_APC_AMT, EXT.PRC_PTCT_DISC_APC_AMT AS PRC_PTCT_DISC_APC_AMTS from VRAP.TDISCNT_APC_RPT TAR, -- This table will have all MODEL/RPT/HVST associated with APC Snapshots for that period VRAP.VRPT_CD VR, -- We join to bring in only REBATED reports as VRAP.TDISCNT_APC_RPT will have Default Exclusion reports too VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM EXT, -- To get the claim information for that RPT and HVST that are already dead 99 VRAP.TDISCNT_PERIOD TP, -- Joined to get the Quarter ID which is VRAP.TDISCNT_APC_RPT, since the RECON can be for any Period Monthly or Quarterly VRAP.RCNT_RECN_PARAM PARM where EXT.RECN_GID = PARM.RECN_GID-- Bring only CV Recons that the process is running, from Param table AND EXT.RECN_SCRB_CD = $$PARM_SCRB_CD -- Dead Claims only (Dropped at one point after APC) --- Even if the claim was part of next next harvest, it will 99 in this Harvest but the lookup will work only for new claim which is not part of Previous Invoice AND TP.PERIOD_ID = PARM.PERIOD_ID --Period ID from Param Table, it is only one period at the time AND TAR.QUARTER_ID = TP.QUARTER_ID-- QUARTER ID is the join to TDISCNT_APC_RPT for that period in the above filter AND VR.RPT_CD_NM LIKE 'R%' -- Only Rebates reports AND VR.RPT_CD = TAR.RPT_TYP_CD -- Only Rebated reports AND TAR.RPT_ID = PARM.RPT_ID and TAR.HVST_ID = EXT.HVST_ID -- Harvest as part of APC snapshot and TAR.RPT_ID = EXT.RPT_ID -- Reports as part of APC snapshot AND EXT.RPT_ID = PARM.RPT_ID -- limit for reports in parametetr table --Run only for reports that the CV is currently processing with ur; --SQL Override

Performs number of inserts and update: 1.Inserts and Updates(Post-SQL on Target) into VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM for copy-void reconciliations. HVST_IDs and RECN_GIDs are joined from RCNT_RECN_PARAM table Sources: VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM -- Only HVST_IDs (INV_IDs) that have been voided. VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM_STG -- Has ALL HVST_IDs, but only NEW HVST_IDs (HVST_IDs not present in VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM) are pulled into the mapping. Targets: VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM -- The mapping inserts and updates copy-voided claims.
2. Post-SQL on the target updates OLD INV_IDs with NEW INV_IDs on HVST_IDs that were retained.
3. Post-SQL updates INV_ID on VRAP.RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM_AUDT. 4. Post-SQL updates INV_ID on VRAP.RCNT_RECN_CLM_ASSC. 5. Post-SQL updates VRAP.RCNT_RECN_VAR to account for voided claims that had VARIANCES. 6. Post-SQL updates VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSPT to account for voided claims that had DISPUTES.
SESSION.NAME: s_m_CASH_InsertUpdate_RCNT_RECN_EXTN_CLM_CopyVoid
